UPDATE-11/1/08 1:32pm est:i have replaced the old file with the new on with slight map tweaks so if you downloaded before today redownload this map.

My Second Release,again another quick map(about 8 hours)
i liked how this one turned out because its simple and to the point.
i hope it plays well.

6-24 players

no weps on map

there is a buy zone

made for gun game

2 "half box" sniping positions

pretty much un-campable spawn (not tested)

Version 1.0,more version 2.0 coming out soon.  (i will replace this map with the updated version,not the 2.0 so check for a redownload)
